properties.Title: Special Weather Statement In Effect
properties.Summary:
Description: 10 to 15 cm of snow possible tonight into Thursday morning. For the air quality index in Montréal, visit the Réseau de surveillance de la qualité de l’air de la Ville de Montréal’s website at www.rsqa.qc.ca (french only).
